span.p:
Scheduled detections (PowerQuery)
DROP (below p05), SPIKE (above p95), NEW (no baseline);
live 24h volume vs the baseline table

Ingest-volume baselines (savelookup)
one table per level: per-source and/or per-device;
avg, stddev, p05, p95 of event volume

Per-level refresh flows (1 per baseline)
staggered daily from LOCAL midnight;
source 00:00, device 00:30; savelookup LRQ

Ingest Health Notifier, run last
daily; check each owned flow's latest state;
email Ops Support if any is not Completed

SILENT watchdog (per level)
anti-join LRQ: baseline vs live volume;
post OCSF alert when an established feed is dark
